Read and follow AGENTS.md. Never replace agents/__init__.py with a normal package initializer because it bridges the local specialist modules and the upstream OpenAI Agents SDK package. Keep model names in configuration, secrets in environment variables, stateless fallback explicit, all public Python typed, guardrails fail-closed, and tests updated. Run ruff check ., mypy ., pytest, and python scripts/test_nexus.py --dry-run before completion.
